items.badge_description: Raise your glass and join Untappd this Pride Month as we recognize the impact the LGBTQIA+ community has had on the beer industry.
Happy Untappd anniversary to you! Thanks for sticking around and drinking socially with us. Cheers! That's 4 years on Untappd!
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 145 distinct venues!
It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 25 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 6.

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, theres a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 65 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 14!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 160 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 33!
It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly whats on tap! That's 315 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 64!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 145 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 30!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 105 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 22!

items.checkin_comment: &b sneaks up on you. Bitterness grows after the first sip. Easily drinkable.
